   1:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp **** /**
   2:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp — MPR121 Fine Tuner (Phase 2)
   3:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * Daisy Seed — Bit-Bang I2C  (SDA=D12, SCL=D11)
   4:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  *
   5:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * Phase 1 found CDC=16uA CDT=16us as best.
   6:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * This sweep fixes those and varies:
   7:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  *   FFI (first filter iterations): 6, 10, 18, 34
   8:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  *   ESI (electrode sample interval): 1ms, 2ms, 4ms, 8ms
   9:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  *
  10:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * More FFI = more hardware averaging per sample = less noise
  11:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * Slower ESI = more time per sample = more stable readings
  12:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  * Both should increase the effective touch delta through glass.
  13:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp ****  */
  14:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp **** 
  15:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp **** #include "daisy_seed.h"
  16:tools/mpr121_glass_tuner2.cpp **** 
