  15:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** For now connecting the DAC through other internal peripherals is also not supported.
  16:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  **
  17:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** Since the DAC channels have dedicated pins we don't need to pass in a pin config like with
  18:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** other modules. However, it is still important to not try to use the DAC pins for anything else.
  19:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/per/dac.h ****  ** DAC Channel 1 is on PA4, and DAC Channel 2 is on PA5
